---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Partnerships, Sponsorships & Growth Opportunities"
  description="Explore selected ProTreeTrim partnerships, territory sponsorships, advertising opportunities, content collaborations, and local growth asset inquiries."
>
  <section class="partnerships-hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Selected B2B opportunities</p>
      <h1>Partnerships, Sponsorships &amp; Growth Opportunities</h1>
      <span>
        ProTreeTrim™ is building a focused Florida tree-service information,
        referral, and homeowner resource platform. We are open to selected
        conversations with service providers, local sponsors, relevant brands,
        subject-matter contributors, and operators exploring similar local
        growth assets.
      </span>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#partnership-options">Explore partnership paths</a>
        <a href="#partnership-form">Send an inquiry</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="signal-strip" aria-label="Partnership page positioning">
    <article>
      <strong>Florida-focused</strong>
      <span
        >Built around homeowners, service-market intent, tools, and practical
        local resource paths.</span
      >
    </article>
    <article>
      <strong>Fit-based</strong>
      <span
        >We review partnership ideas for relevance, audience alignment, and
        platform priorities.</span
      >
    </article>
    <article>
      <strong>Multiple paths</strong>
      <span
        >Provider network, territory visibility, sponsorship, content, and
        similar asset discussions.</span
      >
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="platform-intro">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">A broader ProTreeTrim business layer</p>
      <h2>A focused Florida platform open to aligned growth conversations.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="intro-copy">
      <p>
        ProTreeTrim™ was created to help Florida homeowners move from tree-care
        questions to safer next steps: local service pathways, practical guides,
        storm-readiness resources, county-level planning notes, and
        decision-support tools. As the platform grows, selected partnership
        models can strengthen that ecosystem.
      </p>
      <p>
        This page is not a generic ad-buy form. It is a controlled entry point
        for business inquiries that may fit the ProTreeTrim™ audience, market
        structure, and long-term growth direction.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section
    id="partnership-options"
    class="options-section"
    aria-label="Partnership options"
  >
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Partnership paths</p>
      <h2>Five ways to start the right conversation.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="options-grid">
      <article class="option-card network-card">
        <span>01</span>
        <h3>Tree Service Partner Network</h3>
        <p>
          Licensed and independently operated tree-service professionals
          interested in referral, dispatch, or service-coverage conversations
          should begin with our dedicated partner network page.
        </p>
        <a href="/join-network/">Visit Join Network →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="option-card">
        <span>02</span>
        <h3>City or Territory Sponsorship Opportunities</h3>
        <p>
          We are open to selected conversations around city-level, county-level,
          or territory-based visibility opportunities within the ProTreeTrim™
          ecosystem, subject to fit, availability, and platform priorities.
        </p>
        <a href="#partnership-form">Discuss a territory opportunity →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="option-card">
        <span>03</span>
        <h3>Advertising &amp; Sponsorship</h3>
        <p>
          Relevant brands may inquire about clearly disclosed sponsorship
          models, selective banner placements, or brand-supported educational
          resources that make sense for Florida homeowners and property
          decision-makers.
        </p>
        <a href="#partnership-form">Share a sponsorship idea →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="option-card">
        <span>04</span>
        <h3>Content &amp; Resource Collaborations</h3>
        <p>
          We welcome selected conversations with experts, organizations, and
          industry professionals who can contribute practical insight,
          co-developed resources, or homeowner-friendly educational value.
        </p>
        <a href="#partnership-form">Propose a resource collaboration →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="option-card growth-card">
        <span>05</span>
        <h3>Interested in a Similar Local Growth Asset?</h3>
        <p>
          ProTreeTrim™ is a focused local growth asset built around search
          intent, useful content, conversion pathways, and service-market
          structure. We may be open to select conversations with founders,
          operators, or brands exploring a similar model in another local
          service category or geography.
        </p>
        <strong
          >This is not a standard website package. It is a fit-based discussion
          for serious local growth opportunities.</strong
        >
        <a href="#partnership-form">Start a growth asset inquiry →</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="audience-section" aria-label="Who should reach out">
    <div class="audience-card dark">
      <p class="eyebrow">Who should reach out?</p>
      <h2>Best fit for serious, aligned inquiries</h2>
      <span>
        The form below is designed for businesses and professionals with a clear
        collaboration idea, market focus, or expansion question — not
        one-size-fits-all advertising requests.
      </span>
    </div>

    <div class="audience-grid">
      <article>
        <strong>Tree-service operators</strong>
        <span
          >Network, territory, referral, or service-coverage discussions.</span
        >
      </article>
      <article>
        <strong>Local sponsors</strong>
        <span>City, county, or Florida-market visibility conversations.</span>
      </article>
      <article>
        <strong>Relevant brands</strong>
        <span>Advertising or sponsor-supported resources with clear fit.</span>
      </article>
      <article>
        <strong>Experts &amp; organizations</strong>
        <span
          >Content, safety, homeowner education, or resource collaborations.</span
        >
      </article>
      <article>
        <strong>Founders &amp; operators</strong>
        <span
          >Similar local growth asset conversations for serious opportunities.</span
        >
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section
    id="partnership-form"
    class="form-section"
    aria-label="Partnership inquiry form"
  >
    <div class="form-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Partnership inquiry</p>
      <h2>Tell us what you are exploring</h2>
      <p>
        Use this form for partnership, sponsorship, resource, territory, or
        similar local growth asset discussions. For tree-service contractor
        applications, the dedicated <a href="/join-network/"
          >Join Network page</a
        > remains the best starting point.
      </p>
      <div class="form-note">
        <strong>Helpful details to include</strong>
        <span
          >Your company, target geography, audience fit, proposed collaboration
          model, and desired next step.</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <form action="/api/partnerships/" method="POST" class="partnership-form">
      <div style="display:none;" aria-hidden="true">
        <input type="text" name="fax_number" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" />
      </div>

      <div class="field-grid two-up">
        <label>
          <span>Name *</span>
          <input
            type="text"
            name="name"
            placeholder="Jane Doe"
            required
            maxlength="80"
          />
        </label>
        <label>
          <span>Company *</span>
          <input
            type="text"
            name="company"
            placeholder="Company or organization"
            required
            maxlength="120"
          />
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="field-grid two-up">
        <label>
          <span>Email *</span>
          <input
            type="email"
            name="email"
            placeholder="jane@company.com"
            required
            maxlength="120"
          />
        </label>
        <label>
          <span>Phone</span>
          <input
            type="tel"
            name="phone"
            placeholder="(555) 000-0000"
            maxlength="30"
          />
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="field-grid two-up">
        <label>
          <span>Website</span>
          <input
            type="url"
            name="website"
            placeholder="https://example.com"
            maxlength="240"
          />
        </label>
        <label>
          <span>Inquiry type *</span>
          <select name="inquiry_type" required>
            <option value="">Select one</option>
            <option value="Tree Service Partner Network"
              >Tree Service Partner Network</option
            >
            <option value="City or Territory Sponsorship"
              >City or Territory Sponsorship</option
            >
            <option value="Advertising or Brand Sponsorship"
              >Advertising or Brand Sponsorship</option
            >
            <option value="Content or Resource Collaboration"
              >Content or Resource Collaboration</option
            >
            <option value="Similar Local Growth Asset Inquiry"
              >Similar Local Growth Asset Inquiry</option
            >
            <option value="Other Partnership Opportunity"
              >Other Partnership Opportunity</option
            >
          </select>
        </label>
      </div>

      <label>
        <span>Message *</span>
        <textarea
          name="message"
          rows="7"
          placeholder="Tell us about your company, target market or geography, and the type of partnership or opportunity you would like to discuss."
          required
          maxlength="3000"></textarea>
      </label>

      <button type="submit">Send partnership inquiry</button>
      <p class="privacy-copy">
        By submitting this form, you agree that ProTreeTrim™ may contact you
        regarding this inquiry. Please review our <a href="/privacy/"
          >Privacy Policy</a
        > for more information.
      </p>
    </form>
  </section>

  <section class="closing-note">
    <strong>Selected opportunities only.</strong>
    <span>
      ProTreeTrim™ reviews inquiries for relevance, timing, audience fit, and
      platform priorities. Submission does not guarantee acceptance, placement,
      exclusivity, or a commercial engagement.
    </span>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .partnerships-hero {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #164b34 0%, #082d20 72%);
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 8rem) 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 6px solid #f25a06;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 1020px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .eyebrow,
  .partnerships-hero p,
  .section-heading p,
  .audience-card p,
  .form-copy p:first-child {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    color: #ffb703;
    font-weight: 900;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
  }

  .partnerships-hero h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 6rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
  }

  .partnerships-hero span {
    display: block;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
    color: #bbf7d0;
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2vw, 1.3rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 2.2rem;
  }

  .hero-actions a,
  .option-card a,
  .partnership-form button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 3.3rem;
    padding: 0 1.4rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #f25a06;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 900;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 35px rgba(242, 90, 6, 0.24);
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .hero-actions a:nth-child(2) {
    background: #e8fff1;
    color: #0f3f2a;
    border: 1px solid #b7f7ca;
    box-shadow: none;
  }

  .signal-strip,
  .platform-intro,
  .options-section,
  .audience-section,
  .form-section,
  .closing-note {
    max-width: 1160px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    padding-right: 1.5rem;
  }

  .signal-strip {
    margin-top: -2.1rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .signal-strip article,
  .option-card,
  .audience-grid article,
  .partnership-form,
  .form-note,
  .closing-note {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #dbe7df;
    border-radius: 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 22px 52px rgba(8, 45, 32, 0.08);
  }

  .signal-strip article {
    padding: 1.4rem;
  }

  .signal-strip strong,
  .audience-grid strong,
  .form-note strong,
  .closing-note strong {
    display: block;
    color: #0f3f2a;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
  }

  .signal-strip span,
  .audience-grid span,
  .form-note span,
  .closing-note span {
    display: block;
    color: #526253;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 0.96rem;
  }

  .platform-intro {
    padding-top: clamp(4rem, 7vw, 6rem);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(320px, 0.95fr);
    gap: 2.25rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .platform-intro h2,
  .section-heading h2,
  .audience-card h2,
  .form-copy h2 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #0f3f2a;
    font-size: clamp(2.15rem, 4.4vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.045em;
  }

  .intro-copy {
    background: #f2fff5;
    border: 1px solid #c9efd4;
    border-radius: 28px;
    padding: 1.7rem;
  }

  .intro-copy p,
  .option-card p,
  .audience-card span,
  .form-copy > p:not(.eyebrow) {
    color: #405443;
    line-height: 1.78;
    font-size: 1.03rem;
  }

  .intro-copy p:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .intro-copy p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .options-section,
  .audience-section,
  .form-section {
    padding-top: clamp(4rem, 7vw, 6rem);
  }

  .section-heading {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .options-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1.2rem;
  }

  .option-card {
    padding: 1.8rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .option-card > span {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-width: 3rem;
    min-height: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #e8fff1;
    color: #0f3f2a;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .option-card h3 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #0f3f2a;
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.4vw, 2rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .option-card p {
    margin: 1rem 0 1.2rem;
  }

  .option-card a {
    margin-top: auto;
    min-height: 2.9rem;
    padding: 0 1.15rem;
    font-size: 0.94rem;
  }

  .network-card {
    border-color: #b7f7ca;
  }

  .growth-card {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f3f2a 0%, #082d20 100%);
    border-color: #0f3f2a;
  }

  .growth-card > span {
    background: #ffb703;
    color: #102c1f;
  }

  .growth-card h3,
  .growth-card p {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .growth-card strong {
    display: block;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    color: #bbf7d0;
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .audience-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(320px, 0.9fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
    gap: 1.2rem;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .audience-card {
    border-radius: 32px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .audience-card.dark {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f3f2a 0%, #082d20 100%);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .audience-card.dark h2 {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .audience-card.dark span {
    display: block;
    color: #bbf7d0;
    margin-top: 1.2rem;
  }

  .audience-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .audience-grid article {
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }

  .audience-grid article:last-child {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
  }

  .form-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(320px, 0.85fr) minmax(0, 1.15fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .form-copy {
    position: sticky;
    top: 120px;
  }

  .form-copy > p:not(.eyebrow) a,
  .privacy-copy a {
    color: #f25a06;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .form-note {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.3rem;
    box-shadow: none;
    background: #f2fff5;
  }

  .partnership-form {
    padding: 1.65rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .field-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .field-grid.two-up {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }

  .partnership-form label {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.45rem;
  }

  .partnership-form label > span {
    color: #526253;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .partnership-form input,
  .partnership-form select,
  .partnership-form textarea {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px solid #cfded3;
    background: #fff;
    min-height: 3.2rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 0.95rem;
    color: #1f3024;
    font: inherit;
    outline: none;
  }

  .partnership-form textarea {
    min-height: 11.5rem;
    resize: vertical;
  }

  .partnership-form input:focus,
  .partnership-form select:focus,
  .partnership-form textarea:focus {
    border-color: #1b4332;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(27, 67, 50, 0.09);
  }

  .partnership-form button {
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .privacy-copy {
    margin: 0;
    color: #68786b;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .closing-note {
    margin-top: clamp(4rem, 7vw, 6rem);
    margin-bottom: 10rem;
    padding-top: 1.4rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.4rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(180px, 0.35fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
    background: #fffaf0;
    border-color: #f6d992;
    box-shadow: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .signal-strip,
    .platform-intro,
    .audience-section,
    .form-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .form-copy {
      position: static;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .signal-strip,
    .options-grid,
    .audience-grid,
    .field-grid.two-up,
    .closing-note {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .growth-card,
    .audience-grid article:last-child {
      grid-column: auto;
    }

    .signal-strip {
      margin-top: 1.2rem;
    }

    .partnerships-hero {
      padding-top: 4.5rem;
      padding-bottom: 4.5rem;
    }

    .option-card,
    .audience-card,
    .partnership-form {
      padding: 1.35rem;
    }

    .closing-note {
      margin-bottom: 9rem;
    }
  }
</style>
